window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Would you fall in love again? </p><p>How would you react if someone you love suddenly calls you to convey a message of her engagement and moves out of your life? </p><p>Even the last thread of hope tears up and they are apart. </p><p>Priety is gone and HE remains a mere spectator watching the tide of the time rising high against and shattering all his dreams. </p><p>Will he be able to fight out this hard situation? </p><p>Will he opt for self destruction, making his life hell? Or will he ever take a chance of searching for love again? </p><p>An exquisite beauty slowly and steadily moves into his life, and there begins emotional battle between present and beautiful past. </p><p>Will he be able to replace Past with desired Present? </p><p>What if the same thing happens again? </p><p>Listen and get to know how HE narrates 'I Will Love Once Again'. </p>"; 
